consider
Discworld player help
consider

Name
.SI 5
consider - Consider how worthwhile it is to attack something.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
consider <thing>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Consider is the command used to see if the monster you are thinking
about attacking is too high or too low a level for you.  Of course I
know all of you are insane.  But don't complain if the dragon kills you
ok?
.EP

Examples
.SI 5
> consider dragon
You would have to insane to attack the dragon!
> consider rat
The rat is an easy target.
.EI

See also
.SI 5
stop, cast, spells, consider
.EI
